WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.200
Each circle is a category.

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:07.200
Drag each tile to the overlap it belongs in.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.000
This tile fits two categories, so it goes between them.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
If a tile is wrong, it bounces back.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.200
Keep placing tiles where the overlap matches.

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:26.935
When all 4 answers are placed, the board checks automatically.
